{"tid":1902431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到五毛 / 熱狗開post千祈唔好用不推文回應","createTime":"2020-02-28T10:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T10:57:33.000Z","uid":254456,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1d414feaa605d3f2d5efb45236547a0c30471582","tid":1902431,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:25:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係要直情唔回應</span><br />\n<br />\n根據連仔所講<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>[置頂] LIHKG 常見問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eobQcT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eobQcT</a><br />\n#5 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同一個人最多只可以推文推四次<br />\n<br />\n推完四次之後<br />\n<br />\n一定要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其他人回應</span><br />\n<br />\n先至可以再推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果你用不推文回應<br />\n<br />\n其實係間接幫緊五毛 / 熱狗推post</span><br />\n<br />\n你回應佢間接令到熱門少咗一個行動<br />\n<br />\n例子 : <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTL55hr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTL55hr.jpg&h=2fd870d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jrAeeaV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjrAeeaV.jpg&h=b42649d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以見到引戰post<br />\n<br />\n唔好再用不推文<br />\n<br />\n係要直情唔回應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039f48a5b9654d22ee435bddeeb9b42cfce745a7","tid":1902431,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918b3c1b4d963969ddd4bd1a6666112d99cb4aaa","tid":1902431,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor